### Create a deployment

```
Example Request with Droplet
```

```shell
curl "https://api.example.org/v3/deployments" \
-X POST \
-H "Authorization: bearer [token]" \
-H "Content-type: application/json" \
-d '{
  "droplet": {
    "guid": "[droplet-guid]"
  },
  "strategy": "rolling",
  "relationships": {
    "app": {
      "data": {
        "guid": "[app-guid]"
      }
    }
  }
}'
```

```
Example Request with Revision
```

```shell
curl "https://api.example.org/v3/deployments" \
